headline: Tesla names Europe executive to head global sales, Bloomberg News reports

The move follows ‌the departure of Tesla's head of North American sales, Raj Jegannathan, marking the latest in a string of executive exits at the EV maker over ⁠the past couple of ‌years.  Tesla did not immediately respond to a Reuters request for comment.
